  "response_text": "At night on a rain-wet city street, a dark blue BMW SUV sits near the curb outside low brick and stucco buildings. The pavement reflects streetlights, traffic signals, and teal and red glows from nearby signs. Small white on-screen text near the bottom reads, “European model shown.” Two adults, mostly silhouetted, approach the vehicle: one stands near the driver’s side by the front of the car, while another, with long hair and a coat, walks toward the passenger side. The BMW’s glossy body and bright front lights stand out against the damp, dim industrial-looking block with barred windows and a red vertical wall light.\n\nThe SUV pulls away from the curb and moves down the empty street. From above, it passes a corner building with a lit entrance and colorful rounded decorations or fixtures, while its headlights cast pale blue-white light across the wet road. The vehicle is then seen from behind on a darker street lined with brick buildings; its distinctive red rear lights form angular, glowing shapes, reflected faintly in the slick pavement. Small white disclaimer text appears along the bottom, stating that all lights shown may not be available on all models.\n\nThe BMW continues through a tunnel or underpass with high pale walls and lane markings. Its headlights shine directly forward, and the front grille with BMW’s twin kidney shape becomes prominent as the SUV advances. The front end fills the view: bright, crisp headlamp shapes, the chrome grille bars, and the deep blue paint catching the tunnel lighting. A following view highlights the rear of the vehicle, including the BMW badge, a license plate reading “TRM205,” and the sculpted red tail lights.\n\nThe SUV emerges onto a quieter, tree-lined residential street at night. It turns or pauses under warm streetlamps, its body outlined by reflections on the damp road and by the glow of its lights. It then reaches a modern home set behind low walls, hedges, and tall trees. From above, the BMW sits in the driveway near landscaped greenery lit by small garden lights, its headlights illuminating the path ahead.\n\nInside the house, a young child with shoulder-length brown hair and a blue top appears at a large window. Warm indoor light from a floor lamp behind the child contrasts with the dark exterior brick wall and night garden outside. The child looks out through the glass, smiling and pressing a hand near their mouth in an excited, pleased gesture; their reflection is visible in the window beside them. Outside, the dark blue BMW X3 rests in the driveway with its headlights still on, the chrome grille and large wheels visible against the softly lit shrubs and trees. An adult is faintly visible inside the vehicle, while the home and car are visually connected by the warm house lights and the vehicle’s cool headlight beams.",
